WaitFrame (script event)
========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type [idThread](Thread\_(scripting)), accessible via [sys](Scripting\_basics#sys) identifier.

Description
-----------

Suspends execution of current [thread](Thread\_(scripting)) for one game frame.

Usage
-----

*[void](Data\_types#void)* waitFrame()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

